  "image_directives": "real motorcycle showroom photography. Bikes lined up under track-style lighting, riders trying on helmets at the gear wall, service tech adjusting a chain on a lift. Show OEM badges (Honda, Yamaha, Suzuki, Kawasaki) where natural. Detail shots of grips, fuel tanks, exhausts. Avoid leather-vest cliche. Real customers throwing a leg over a bike for the first time. Open garage door with bikes parked outside is a strong hero shot.",
